Module  : CMS
Version : 1.0.0
Author  : Maurice Makaay <maurice@phorum.org>

This module adds some CMS-like features to Phorum, making it possible
to use Phorum to build a complete website, pushing the forums to a sub-level.


Installation instructions:
--------------------------

- Unpack the archive;

- Move the directory "custom_index_page" to the directory "mods"
  within your Phorum installation;

- Login as administrator in Phorum's administrative interface and
  go to the "Modules" section;

- Enable the module "Custom Index Page".

